#####################################
## REQUIRED INPUT FILES/DIRECTORIES
#####################################

* params/params.tcsh: script used to load all tools and dependencies using "module load"

* fastq/: put all fastq.gz or bam files here (symbolic links are accepted as well)

* sample-sheet.tsv: 
This file can be created automatically by ./code/create-sample-sheet.tcsh script and then edited manually if necessary. Has the following required fields:
- sample (e.g. CUTLL1-DMSO-CTCF-rep1)
- control (e.g. CUTLL1-DMSO-Input-rep1)
- group (e.g. CUTLL1-DMSO-CTCF)
- fastq-r1
- fastq-r2
- genome (e.g. hg19, mm10)
- fragmentation-size

